HEADWORD: Dynam
<hw>Dy"nam</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Cf. F.
<ets>dyname</ets>. See <er>Dynamic</er>.]</ety> <def>A unit of measure
